-- PBOC's Zhou Says China Needs Conditions for Banking Reform, News Reports
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-09-26T23:58:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-26/pboc-s-zhou-says-china-needs-conditions-for-banking-reform-news-reports.html
Chinese central bank governor Zhou
Xiaochuan said the nation needs to provide conditions for banks
to improve asset management, the Shanghai Securities News
reported.  The nation should supply banks with tools for flexible and
effective adjustments of their balance sheet, the newspaper
reported today, citing Zhou.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
